item.title: The New Staff
item.dc:creator: @The_Reaper_X The Reaper X
item.description:
@The_Reaper_X wrote:

casey.:

[quote]I haven’t been online to see your rebuttal.

Lies. I’ve checked your profile and you’ve viewed the site since that response.[/quote]Are you really that ignorant? It’s called being idle, else I didn’t think to check for replies to my post. I honestly did not read what you said to give a response. What causes you to go into a fucking compulsive search on my profile is beyond me. I suggest you stop making such idiotic accusations.

I’ve given my explanation on the forum activity, and once again, you should already know this. I don’t know why you’re being so dramatic and cocky. You’re incredibly pessimistic about this community, yet you “love it” in it’s entirety. It’s a bit of a contradiction, wouldn’t you say so? Also, your attitude is incredibly condescending, yet you offer nothing to back yourself up but your registry date. I had respect for you over a lot of people in this community, until whatever it was that provoked you to be such an idiot in this thread.

Moparscape is on it’s way to better opportunities. Things are much more organized and the staff in position right now are incredibly focused on the community. I don’t see how anything could go wrong.

Read full topic
